---
title: Bacon Apple Breakfast Pizza with Ricotta and Balsamic Onion
description: Pizza for breakfast doesn’t have to mean a cold, leftover slice. In fact, it can be a beautifully toasty and golden crust, a mouthwatering spread of creamy ricotta, and, because it’s breakfast, a cascade of bacon and apple pieces. Trust us, after trying this made-for-mornings version, you’ll understand why pizza is a perfect food at any time of day.
